20has%20already%20done%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Putin%20also%20ordered%20his%20troops%20to%20press%20their%20advantage%20on%20the%20battlefield%20and%20step%20up%20their%20attacks.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20saying%20not%20so%20long%20ago%3A%20'We%20will%20finish%20them%20off.'%20Now%20there%20are%20reasons%20to%20believe%20that%20we%20will%20indeed%20finish%20them%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20gradually%2C%20not%20as%20fast%20as%20some%20would%20like%2C%20but%20nevertheless%20persistently%20and%20confidently%20moving%20toward%20achieving%20all%20the%20goals%20stated%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20special%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUKRAINE%20BRACES%20FOR%20IMPACT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Andriy%20Yermak%2C%20Ukrainian%20presidency's%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRussia%20is%20trying%20to%20derail%20the%20path%20to%20peace%20by%20choosing%20to%20continue%20the%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20President%20Zelensky%20rushed%20to%20Paris%20to%20meet%20Ukraine's%20key%20European%20backers%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20strike%20a%20unified%20position%20of%20support%20against%20President%20Putin's%20aggression%20as%20well%20as%20President%20Trump's%20overhaul%20of%20US'%20policy%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20he%20claims%20is%20leaning%20towards%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%20that%20meeting%20in%20Paris%2C%20President%20Zelensky%20said%20he%20was%20left%20with%20%26quot%3Bmany%20more%20questions%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bvery%20few%20answers%26quot%3B.%20The%20talks%20were%20led%20by%20France%20and%20Britain%20on%20a%20possible%20European%20troop%20deployment%20as%20part%20of%20any%20wider%20ceasefire%20or%20peace%20deal.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743159240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2