ernment-employees%2Farticleshow%2F119650742.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20Cabinet%2C%20led%20by%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20approved%20a%202%25%20increase%20in%20Dearness%20Allowance%20and%20Dearness%20Relief%20for%20Central%20Government%20employees%20and%20pensioners%2C%20effective%20January%201%2C%202025.%20The%20rate%20rise%20from%2053%25%20to%2055%25%20aims%20to%20combat%20inflation%2C%20impacting%20over%20115%20lakh%20individuals%2C%20with%20costs%20estimated%20at%20Rs%206%2C614.04%20crore%20annually.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcabinet-approves-2-dearness-allowance-hike-for-central-government-employees%2Farticleshow%2F119650742.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Centre%20Raises%20Dearness%20Allowance%20For%20Union%20Government%20Employees%20By%202%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20salary%20increase%20for%20central%20government%20employees%20ahead%20of%20the%208th%20Pay%20Commission%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20approved%20a%202%20per%20cent%20increase%20in%20dearness%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20revision%2C%20the%20dearness%20allowance%20(DA)%20will%20rise%20from%2053%20per%20cent%20to%2055%20per%20cent.%20DA%20is%20provided%20to%20government%20employees%20to%20compensate%20them%20against%20price%20rise%20because%20of%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%203%20per%20cent%20hike%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20DA%20increased%20to%2053%20per%20cent%20of%20basic%20pay%20in%20the%20last%20update.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%208th%20Pay%20Commission%2C%20which%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20Centre%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20revised%20the%20wages%20and%20allowances%20of%20central%20government%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20formal%20constitution%20of%20the%20commission%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20cha