0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-loan-rates-today-friday-28-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743156901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea2eda6080194819fdcf05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-loan-rates-today-friday-28-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20personal%20loan%20with%20the%20best%20rate%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20done%20the%20research%20for%20you%20and%20found%20the%20lowest%20personal%20loan%20interest%20rates.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Business%20Insider)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-loan-rates-today-friday-28-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Europe%20says%20'emerging%20threats'%20mean%20people%20should%20stockpile%20enough%20supplies%20for%2072%20hours.%20Here's%20what%20experts%20suggest.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20rearranging%20the%20nonperishable%20food%20at%20the%20food%20bank%20in%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e56b01b8b41a9673fbdc33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20EU%20advised%20its%20citizens%20to%20stockpile%20three-days%20worth%20of%20supplies%20in%20case%20of%20major%20crises.%3Cp%3EFilippoBacci%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20European%20Union%20advised%20citizens%20to%20stockpile%2072%20hours%20of%20supplies%20for%20potential%20crises.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20strategy%20to%20enhance%20Europe's%20response%20to%20emerging%20threats.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20advise%20stockpiling%20supplies%20to%20last%20much%20longer%20than%2072%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Union%20issued%20a%20stark%20new%20advisory%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20advising%20people%20to%20stockpile%2072%20hours'%20worth%20of%20supplies%20in%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bthreats%20and%20crises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20part%20of%20a%20wide-ranging%20strategy%20designed%20to%20%26quot%3Benhance%20Europe's%20capability%20to%20prevent%20and%20respond%20to%20emerging%20threats%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20EU%20did%20not%20specifically%20mention%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20comes%20amid%20growing%20concerns%20over%20Russian%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20face%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20external%20security%20challenges%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20hybrid%20attacks%20in%20our%20common%20European%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kaja%20Kallas%2C%20the%20EU's%20representative%20for%20foreign%20affairs%20and%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU's%20strategy%20involves%20disaster%20preparation%20at%20the%20level%20of%20international%20and%20military%20cooperation%2C%20and%20for%20essential%20services%20such%20as%20hospitals%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20telecommunications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20most%20eye-catching%20advice%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20for%20the%20EU's%20450%20million%20people%20%E2%80%94%20is%20for%20everyone%20to%20have%20an%20emergency%20stockpile%20of%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea447cef-7470-4b08-b665-55bde4e92ded%5C%22%3EStockpile%20what%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20well-prepared%20American%20families%20in%20the%20path%20of%20hurricanes%2C%20Europeans%20have%20not%20typically%20made%20it%20a%20priority%20to%20draw%20up%20plans%20for%20emergencies%2C%20said%20Lucy%20Easthope%2C%20a%20leading%20advisor%20in%20emergency%20planning%20and%20disaster%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeventy-two%20hours%20of%20supplies%20has%20long%20been%20the%20standard%20advice%20issued%20by%20authorities%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20the%20messaging%20today%20is%20it's%20not%20really%20fit%20for%20anything%20other%20than%20probably%20a%20short%20weather%20or%20power-based%20outage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EU's%20preparedness%20and%20crisis%20management%20commissioner%2C%20Hadja%20Lahbib%2C%20said%20it's%20up%20to%20each%20member%20state%20to%20define%20what%20to%20stockpile%20%26quot%3Baccording%20to%20their%20geographical%20and%20geostrategic%20positions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIlan%20Kelman%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20disaster%20and%20health%20at%20University%20College%20London%2C%20outlined%20some%20basic%20advice%20to%20BI%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20keeping%20plenty%20of%20bottled%20water%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20for%20drinking%2C%20it's%20also%20for%20hand%20washing%2C%20for%20toilets%20and%20other%20hygiene%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20gallon%20of%20water%20per%20person%20a%20day%20is%20needed%20just%20for%20drinking%2C%20according%20to%20Swrajit%20Sarkar%2C%20a%20specialist%20in%20emergency%20nutrition%20at%20City%20St%20George's%2C%20University%20of%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20ideally%2C%20all%20five%20main%20food%20groups%20should%20be%20covered%20across%20non-perishable%20items%20including%20nuts%2C%20lentils%2C%20dried%20fruits%2C%20and%20canned%20beans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20dairy%20alternatives%2C%20Sarkar%20recommended%20powdered%20or%20ultra-heat-treated%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20cheese%20lovers%2C%20he%20said%20that%20waxed%20cheeses%2C%20like%20Babybel%20or%20Gouda%2C%20have%20a%20very%20long%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGranola%20or%20protein%20bars%20keep%20well%2C%20make%20good%20snacks%20and%20deliver%20energy%2C%20too%2C%20Sarkar%20said.%20He%20also%20suggests%20dark%20chocolate%2C%20as%20studies%20prove%20it's%20a%20mood%20booster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKelman%20said%20basic%20grain%20staples%20such%20as%20rice%20or%20pasta%20store%20well%2C%20but%20aren't%20easy%20to%20cook%20if%20there's%20no%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeats%20or%20fish%20should%20be%20smoked%20or%20otherwise%20preserved%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20advised%20keeping%20plenty%20of%20starches%20such%20as%20bread%20and%20crackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f12d0803-76d8-4c42-b7d5-b3c6daa52354%5C%22%3ENon-food%20items%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKelman%20said%20people%20should%20try%20to%20ensure%20they%20have%20a%20radio%20%E2%80%94%20either%20battery-powered%20or%20wind-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutgoing%20communication%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20more%20challenging%26quot%3B%20unless%20people%20want%20to%20invest%20in%20walkie-talkies%20or%20shortwave%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoutgoing%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eradios%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHygiene%20items%20such%20as%20sanitary%20pads%2C%20soap%2C%20and%20nappies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20first%20aid%20kits%20and%20essential%20medicine%2C%20are%20also%20a%20must%2C%20Kelman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20light%20%E2%80%94%20and%20power%20%E2%80%94%20are%20important.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20power%20bank%20for%20my%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20Easthope%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20solar-powered%20light%2C%20solar-powered%20torches%2C%20chargeable%20torches.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20safety%20reasons%2C%20she%20recommended%20avoiding%20candles%20or%20indoor%20portable%20cookers%20if%20at%20all%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEasthope%20also%20recommended%20having%20essential%20documents%2C%20like%20passports%20and%20insurance%20papers%2C%20on%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20often%20forgotten%20is%20morale.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%2C%20very%20important%20to%20keep%20the%20mind%20busy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Coloring%20books%2C%20knitting%2C%20and%20board%20games%20%E2%80%94%20any%20entertainment%20that%20doesn't%20use%20electricity%20%E2%80%94%20are%20a%20godsend%20for%20people%20in%20a%20heightened%20state%20of%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be242801-74db-4b7c-addf-21aa47ca093b%5C%22%3E72%20hours%20as%20the%20bare%20minimum%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKelman%20advised%20stocking%20up%20for%20at%20least%20two%20weeks%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20do%20end%20up%20in%20a%20regional%20or%20even%20full-scale%20military%20conflict%2C%20then%20there%20is%20not%20a%20chance%20that%2072%20hours%20of%20supplies%20is%20going%20to%20last%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnything%20that%20takes%20out%20the%20power%20grid%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20missile%20strike%2C%20or%20a%20solar%20flare%20%E2%80%94%20could%20take%20weeks%20to%20fix%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20even%20asking%20people%20to%20have%20three%20days%20of%20extra%20food%20in%20reserve%20may%20be%20beyond%20the%20continent's%20least%20well-off%2C%20Kelman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20tragedy%20is%20that%20many%20people%20cannot%20afford%20to%20put%20enough%20food%20on%20the%20table%20every%20day%2C%20so%20making%20demands%20that%20they%20should%20have%2072%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20or%20two%20weeks%20%E2%80%94%20of%20supplies%20is%20untenable%20in%20today's%20economic%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-warning-stockpile-emergency-supplies-experts-say-pack-preparation-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743156418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e56b7c69253ccddf9a759c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-warning-stockpile-emergency-supplies-experts-say-pack-preparation-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20European%20Union%20is%20advising%20people%20to%20stockpile%2072%20hours'%20worth%20of%20emergency%20supplies%20due%20to%20%26quot%3Bemerging%20threats.%26quot%3B%20BI%20asked%20experts%20what%20they%20suggest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mjankowicz%40businessinsider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz%2CJoshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A34%2C%22canon