the%20same%20luxe%20experience.%20Red%20and%20gold%20boxes%20of%20coffee%20blends%20are%20stacked%20on%20the%20ceiling%2C%20and%20products%20are%20displayed%20on%20shiny%20golden%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20TWG%20Tea%2C%20it%2C%20too%2C%20offers%20affordable%20luxury.%20The%20Bacha%20Coffee%20outlet%20in%20Marina%20Bay%20Sands%2C%20one%20of%20Singapore's%20biggest%20malls%2C%20sells%20croissants%20for%20SG%2410%20and%20pre-packaged%20coffee%20boxes%20for%20SG%2432.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289953a4d-99b5-41a5-b7dd-9edcf8a0000c%5C%22%3EAffordable%20luxury%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETWG%20Tea%20started%20in%20Singapore%20in%202008%20and%20is%20now%20sold%20in%20over%20100%20locations%20globally.%20Bacha%20Coffee%2C%20founded%20in%20Morocco%20in%201910%20and%20revived%20by%20V3%20Gourmet%20in%202019%2C%20sells%20products%20in%2028%20stores%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBouqdib%20says%20he%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20tea%20when%20he%20was%20a%20child%2C%20living%20next%20to%20the%20Chinese%20Embassy%20in%20Rabat%2C%20Morocco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20always%20gave%20us%2C%20as%20the%20neighbor%2C%20some%20teas%2C%26quot%3B%20Bouqdib%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Morocco%2C%20normally%20we%20have%20this%20tradition%20of%20drinking%20tea%20with%20mint%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20sugar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20For%20him%2C%20Chinese%20tea%20had%20a%20very%20%26quot%3Bunique%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bparticular%26quot%3B%20taste%20%E2%80%94%20one%20he'll%20never%20forget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20assortment%20of%20products%20in%20Bacha%20Coffee%2C%20including%20coffee%2C%20pastries%2C%20and%20cream.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d3d3dc585f1dff88b22386%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBouqdib%20said%20he%20wants%20Bacha%20to%20be%20a%20place%20where%20customers%20can%20%26quot%3Bdiscover%20other%20countries%2C%20other%20cultures%2C%20just%20in%20one%20store.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EV3%20Gourmet%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20experience%20led%20Bouqdib%20down%20the%20path%20to%20creating%20a%20beautiful%20place%20packed%20to%20the%20brim%20with%20teas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20he%20expanded%20to%20coffee%2C%20with%20Bacha.%20He%20wanted%20to%20have%20%26quot%3Bcoffee%20around%20the%20world%20in%20one%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20customers%20can%20%26quot%3Bdiscover%20other%20countries%2C%20other%20cultures%2C%20just%20in%20one%20store.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22625d7db2-b9c3-4f0c-84b4-fb6bfd72ab0c%5C%22%3EYoung%20people%20are%20good%20for%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBouqdib%20said%20that%20young%20people%20%E2%80%94%20even%20those%20without%20deep%20pockets%20%E2%80%94%20are%20good%20for%20TWG%20Tea%20and%20Bacha%20Coffee's%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20price%20his%20products%20so%20that%20children%20or%20students%20with%20some%20spare%20pocket%20money%20could%20buy%20them%20as%20gifts%20or%20to%20pamper%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20SG%2412%20strikes%20you%20as%20a%20lot%20for%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20remember%20that%20Singapore%20is%20a%20country%20where%20a%20flat%20white%20from%20Starbucks%20can%20easily%20cost%20you%20SG%249%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20for%20a%20takeaway%20order%20that%20doesn't%20include%20the%20sumptuous%20experience%20of%20a%20TWG.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20the%20fancier%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%20if%20you%20were%20to%20opt%20for%20one%20of%20Singapore's%20premier%20high%20tea%20experiences%2C%20you%20could%20find%20yourself%20shelling%20out%20SG%2498%20for%20tea%20and%20finger%20foods%20at%20the%20Raffle%20Hotel's%20Grand%20Lobby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20prices%20are%20also%20on%20par%20with%20or%20lower%20than%20its%20competitors.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20set%20of%20five%20macarons%20at%20TWG%20Tea's%20outlet%20in%20MBS%20retails%20for%20SG%2412.50.%