l%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20of%20a%20career%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20we're%20not%20the%20ones%20choosing%20it%20%E2%80%94%20can%20bring%20about%20feelings%20of%20anger%2C%20as%20well%20as%20grief%20related%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20professional%20identity%2C%20purpose%2C%20community%2C%20and%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20federal%20employees%20are%20now%20dealing%20with%20these%20heavy%20emotions%20and%20are%20overwhelmed%20from%20now%20needing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhen-can-i-retire%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethink%20about%20a%20retirement%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20once%20assumed%20to%20be%20five%20or%2010%20years%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20lawyer%20and%20retirement%20transition%20expert%2C%20I've%20helped%20many%20career%20professionals%20plan%20for%20what%20comes%20next%20when%20they%20confront%20an%20unplanned%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%2C%20forced%20or%20not%2C%20unprocessed%20anger%20and%20grief%20should%20never%20be%20the%20defining%20features%20of%20one's%20retirement.%20And%20going%20into%20retirement%20without%20proper%20planning%20is%20foreshadowing%20disaster.%20Here%20are%20seven%20steps%20to%20take%20if%20you're%20forced%20to%20retire%20before%20you're%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3f7a710-26bc-4b03-aecd-f3d94e2bdd51%5C%22%3E1.%20Recognize%20feelings%20of%20anger%20and%20grief%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20through%20these%20negative%20emotions%20can%20seem%20deeply%20unpleasant%2C%20processing%20your%20anger%20and%20grieving%20these%20losses%20are%20important%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planner-mistakes-planning-early-retirement-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20positive%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20thing%2C%20unprocessed%20anger%20and%20grief%20can%20harden%20into%20a%20form%20of%20permanent%20bitterness%20and%20risk%20defining%20a%20rewarding%20multi-decade%20career%20by%20one%20moment%20%E2%80%94%20its%20endpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22167a7817-b544-4219-ad0b-3e26afc7c255%5C%22%3E2.%20Understand%20retirement%20can%20be%20stressful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERetirement%20is%20a%20major%20life%20change%20and%20can%20be%20a%20stressful%20experience%20for%20everyone%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20the%20circumstances%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stress.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FHolmes-Rahe-Stress-inventory.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResearch%20indicates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20retirement%20can%20be%20among%20life's%20most%20stressful%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20concerned%20about%20who%20you%20will%20be%20or%20how%20your%20life%20will%20work%20in%20retirement%2C%20you're%20not%20alone.%20It%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20connect%20with%20others%20who%20have%20been%20through%20or%20are%20going%20through%20a%20similar%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a29a571-3d23-4f7d-afc6-c6420387ff94%5C%22%3E3.%20Redefine%20your%20identity%20during%20retirement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20regularly%20see%20my%20clients%20struggle%20with%20what%20feels%20like%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20very%20identity%20as%20they%20contemplate%20retirement.%20It's%20common%20to%20build%20your%20identity%20around%20the%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretirement-high-stress-career-restored-my-health-slow-travel-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroles%20that%20you%20play%20in%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20your%20career%20often%20supplies%20one%20or%20more%20of%20those%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20have%20to%20let%20those%20go%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20like%20an%20existential%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20retirement%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20explore%20and%20reconnect%20with%20enduring%20aspects%20of%20your%20identity%20beyond%20just%20your%20career%20roles.%20How%20can%20you%20invest%20more%20in%20other%20ro