.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be5af8da-91a7-4c87-9e57-46065f284f16%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20then%20off%20to%20a%20plane%20if%20I'm%20traveling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20days%20are%20different%20from%20typical%20days.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20fly%20to%20Boston%20to%20speak%20at%20Harvard%20and%20then%20to%20Montreal%20to%20meet%20agencies%20and%20shoot%20content.%20Then%2C%20I%20hop%20from%20Montreal%20to%20New%20York%20to%20shoot%20a%20live%20podcast.%20I%20try%20to%20be%20super%20available%20and%20work%20through%20my%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20speaking%2C%20which%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20content%20creation.%20Between%20organic%20and%20paid%20traffic%2C%20we%20have%20about%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40drinkpoppi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20two%20billion%20views%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20create%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdrinkpoppi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2050%20to%20100%2B%20pieces%20of%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20go%20to%20another%20city%2C%20we'll%20add%20an%20extra%20day%20for%20me%20to%20shoot%20content.%20I'll%20visit%20grocery%20stores%2C%20walk%20up%20and%20down%20the%20streets%2C%20interview%20people%2C%20and%20shoot%20trends%20and%20commercials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20the%20Lakers'%20official%20soda%2C%20so%20I%20became%20their%20honorary%20captain.%20I%20then%20shot%20content%20and%20represented%20our%20big%20launch%20in%20October%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223359%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20couple%20sits%20courtside%20at%20a%20Lakers%20game%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e581ae63d72727e1986d94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllsworth%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Stephen%2C%20at%20a%20Lakers%20game.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Poppi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id