te%20home%2C%20and%20have%20a%20family%20dinner%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECooking%20is%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20things%20to%20do.%20I%20try%20to%20shut%20my%20computer%20when%20I%20get%20home.%20I'm%20with%20my%20family%20for%20at%20least%20one%20hour%20at%20night%2C%20even%20if%20the%20kids%20are%20screaming%2C%20running%20around%2C%20and%20jumping%20on%20the%20tables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20services%20like%20Marley%20Spoon%2C%20where%20all%20the%20ingredients%20are%20there%20and%20you%20can%20make%20dinner%20in%2020%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20a%20busy%20week%2C%20we'll%20stop%20on%20the%20way%20home%20to%20get%20tacos.%20Our%20schedule%20is%20not%20so%20structured%20that%20every%20meal%20has%20to%20be%20perfectly%20cooked%20every%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff79ec05-7a2d-431d-a00d-7c661fc54ffa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20include%20self-care%20in%20my%20schedule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20spending%20time%20with%20my%20kids.%20Working%20out%2C%20meditating%2C%20reading%2C%20or%20other%20traditional%20things%20people%20say%20are%20not%20part%20of%20my%20self-care%20routine.%20I%20love%20rewarding%20myself%20with%20shopping%20and%20getting%20my%20nails%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20loves%20Poppi.%20My%20kids%20have%20at%20least%20two%20cans%20a%20day%2C%20and%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20probably%20drink%20three%20cans%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20a%20Poppi%20fridge%20in%20our%20garage%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20kids%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20ring%20our%20doorbell%20and%20ask%20for%20a%20Poppi.%20We%20go%20through%2050%20to%20100%20cans%20a%20week%20at%20our%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cfd657b-63f1-4efd-a1c6-52c6efb03f61%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20it's%20quickly%20off%20to%20baths%20and%20bedtime%20for%20the%20kids%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223187%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20couple%20sits%20in%20bed%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20pizza%20while%20wearing%20robes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e581ee69253ccddf9a7b60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222390%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllsworth%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Stephen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Poppi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20dinner%2C%20we%20leave%20the%20kitchen%20messy%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20kids.%20We%20read%20books%2C%20do%20a%20puzzle%2C%20and%20try%20not%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20go%20to%20bed%20around%208%20p.m.%2C%20we%20clean%20up%20around%20the%20house.%20I%20then%20get%20in%20bed%20with%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%2C%20put%20on%20a%20show%2C%20and%20the%20computer%20reopens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20emails%2C%20review%20PowerPoint%20decks%2C%20approve%20them%2C%20and%20get%20back%20to%20people%20waiting%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20work%20for%20an%20hour%20or%20two%20while%20watching%20TV%20and%20then%20get%20to%20bed%20around%2011%20p.m.%20Since%20I'm%20a%20night%20owl%2C%20if%20I'm%20in%20the%20groove%2C%20I'll%20work%20until%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20I%20get%20six%20to%20seven%20hours%20of%20sleep%20at%20most.%20Then%20I%20wake%20up%20and%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-poppi-cofounder-cbo-allison-ellsworth-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743152701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e5821769253ccddf9a7b78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-poppi-cofounder-cbo-allison-ellsworth-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Allison%20Ellsworth%20relaunched%20her%20prebiotic%20soda%20brand%20as%20Poppi%20in%20March%202020.%20PepsiCo%20announced%20it%20will%20acquire%20Poppi%20for%20%241.95%20billion%20this%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40insider.c