mself.%20If%20he%20comes%20out%20and%20says%2C%20'they%20are%20all%20our%20players%2C%20and%20just%20like%20me%20batting%20they%20are%20batting%20in%20the%20middle'%2C%20or%20something%20like%20that%20to%20soothe%20the%20crowd%2C%20it%20will%20be%20great%20for%20the%20players%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20quite%20challenging.%20Not%20only%20for%20the%20players%20or%20Chennai%2C%20but%20definitely%20for%20the%20franchise%20itself%2C%20because%20for%20them%20to%20%5Battract%5D%20crowds%20like%20that%2C%20especially%20even%20on%20weekdays%20-%20the%20stands%20are%20full%2C%20the%20engagement%20is%20amazing%3B%20there%20is%20no%20cricketer%20close%20to%20him%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%20They%20have%20not%20built%20up%20any%20other%20guy%20in%20the%20franchise%20to%20pull%20the%20crowds%2C%20because%20it%20has%20always%20revolved%20around%20MS%20Dhoni.%20That%20might%20come%20back%20to%20maybe%20bite%20them%20in%20terms%20of%20branding%20or%20getting%20the%20crowds%20in.%20So%20they%20will%20have%20to%20really%20think%20out%20of%20the%20box%20to%20make%20something%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743149160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F9elo9ie8_ms-dhoni-afp_625x300_24_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-craze-harming-csk-ambati-rayudu-says-internally-lot-of-people-8030005%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20god-like%20figure%20for%20CSK%20fans%2C%20but%20this%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20obsession%20can%20sometimes%20go%20out%20of%20hands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2025%2Fms-dhoni-craze-harming-csk-ambati-rayudu-says-internally-lot-of-people-8030005%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2218%20Million%20Tons%20Of%20'White%20Gold'%20Worth%20%24540%20Billion%20Unearthed%20In%20The%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20lithium%20discovery%20beneath%20California's%20Salton%20Sea%2C%20the%20state's%20largest%20lake%2C%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20transform%20the%20US%20battery%20industry%20and%20advance%20clean%20energy%20ambitions%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Daily%20Galaxy.%20%3C%2Fem%3EScientists%20estimate%20that%20the%20lake%20contains%20approximately%2018%20million%20tons%20of%20lithium%2C%20a%20key%20component%20in%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20discovery%20is%20particularly%20timely%20as%20the%20world%20transitions%20to%20EVs%20and%20renewable%20energy%20sources.%20The%20Salton%20Sea's%20lithium%20reserves%20could%20reduce%20the%20nation's%20dependence%20on%20foreign%20lithium%20imports%20and%20support%20the%20production%20of%20batteries%20for%20millions%20of%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Southern%20California's%20Imperial%20County%2C%20the%20Salton%20Sea%20is%20now%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20lithium%20brine%20deposits.%20A%20US%20Department%20of%20Energy-funded%20study%20revealed%20the%20estimated%2018%20million%20tons%2C%20far%20exceeding%20previous%20estimates.%20The%20find%20presents%20both%20significant%20opportunities%20and%20complex%20challenges%20related%20to%20environmental%20risks%20and%20geopolitical%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20McKibben%2C%20a%20geochemistry%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Riverside%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20study's%20authors%2C%20emphasised%20the%20significance%20of%20this%20discovery%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdailygalaxy.com%2F2025%2F01%2Fscientists-find-540-billion-in-white-gold-beneath-a-giant-california-lake%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDaily%20Galaxy%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20lithium%20brine%20deposits%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20could%20make%20the%20United%20States%20completely%20self-sufficient%20in%20lithium%20and%20stop%20importing%20it%20through%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Governor%20Gavin%20Newsom%20has%20already%20dubbed%20the%20Salton%20Sea%20the%20%26quot%3BSaudi%20Arabia%20of%20lithium%26quot%3B%2C%20highlighting%20its%20potential%20to%20position%20the%20U.S.%20as%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20lithium%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20discovery%20is%20monumental%2C%20extracting%20lithium%20from%20the%20Salton%20Sea%20is%20no%20simple%20task.%20The%20process%20involves%20drilling%20geothermal%20production%20wells%20thousands%20of%20feet%20below%20the%20earth's%20surface%20to%20access%20lithium-rich%20brine.%20Once%20the%20lithium%20is%20extracted%2C%20the%20brine%20is%20pumped%20back%20underground.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743148860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Ffsqpjha_lithium_625x300_28_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F18-million-tons-of-white-gold-lithium-worth-540-billion-unearthed-in-the-us-8030739%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20significant%20lithium%20deposit%2C%20estimated%20at%2018%20million%20tons%2C%20has%20been%20discovered%20beneath%20California's%20Salton%20Sea%2C%20potentially%20transforming%20the%20US%20battery%20industry%20and%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20foreign%20lithium%20imports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2F18-million-tons-of-white-gold-lithium-worth-540-billion-unearthed-in-the-us-8030739%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20China%20Is%20Exploiting%20'Failed'%20Projects%20In%20India's%20Neighbourhood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20China%20has%20made%20major%20inroads%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20region%2C%20especially%20through%20infrastructure%20and%20connectivity%20projects.%20This%20has%20intensified%20under%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%20which%20was%20started%20in%202013.%20The%20grand%20projects%20have%20helped%20China%20gain%20major%20strategic%20footholds%20in%20the%20region.%20Here%20are%20some%20key%20ports%20and%20airports%20in%20India's%20neighbourhood%20that%20provide%20China%20with%20a%20strong%20vantage%20position%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%94both%20through%20land%20and%20ocean%E2%80%94and%20challenge%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETwo%20Dead%20Projects%20In%20Sri%20Lanka%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20had%20looked%20to%20Beijing%20for%20a%20loan%20to%20build%20its%20ambitious%20Hambantota%20port.%20China%20spent%20around%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20total%20towards%20this.%20The%20China%20Export%20Import%20Bank%20extended%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20loan%20(%24306%20million)%20at%20the%20rate%20of%206.3%25%2C%20while%20the%20second%20half%20(%24757%20million)%20was%20at%202%25.%20The%20construction%20of%20the%20port%20began%20in%202007%2C%20and%20the%20first%20phase%20was%20completed%20in%202010.%20However%2C%20in%202012%2C%20only%20about%2034%20ships%20docked%20at%20Hambantota.%20As%20the%20port%20was%20not%20financially%20viable%20and%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20continued%20to%20falter%20on%20debt%20repayment%20in%202017%2C%20the%20port%2C%20along%20with%20about%2015%2C000%20acres%20of%20land%20near%20it%2C%20was%20leased%20out%20to%20China.%20Such%20a%20development%20aggravates%20New%20Delhi's%20security%20concerns%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%20a%20strategically%20and%20geopolitically%20critical%20area.%20It%20also%20complements%20China's%20ambitions%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20Mattala%20Rajapaksa%20International%20Airport%20in%20Hambantota%2C%20opened%20in%202013%2C%20was%20also%20built%20with%20a%20Chinese%20loan%20of%20%24206%20million.%20However%2C%20after%20being%20termed%20one%20of%20the%20emptiest%20airports%20in%20the%20world%2C%20it%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20major%20challenge%20for%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government.%20A%20number%20of%20airlines%2C%20even%20after%20signing%20agreements%2C%20have%20stopped%20operating%20flights%20here.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20in%202024%2C%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20the%20airport%20were%20awarded%20to%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20Indian%20and%20Russian%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Gwadar%20Developments%20In%20Pakistan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20all-weather%20friendship%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20has%20been%20a%20major%20security%20concern%20for%20New%20Delhi%20since%20the%201960s.%20China%20has%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20helping%20Islamabad%20financially%20and%20militarily%2C%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20form%20of%20technology%20transfer.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20China%2C%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20China%20Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%2C%20has%20invested%20in%20building%20a%20deep-sea%20port%20at%20Gwadar%2C%20which%20was%20completed%20in%202007.%20However%2C%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20the%20port%20saw%20only%2022%20ships.%20Pakistan%20owes%20Beijing%20about%20%2410%20billion%20in%20debt%20for%20it%20now.%20No%20surprises%20then%20that%20in%202017%2C%20Islamabad%20leased%20Gwadar%20to%20Beijing%20for%2040%20years.%20The%20China%20Overseas%20Port%20Holding%20Company%20(COPHC)%20is%20to%20take%20care%20of%20development%20and%20day-to-day%20operations%20there.%20This%20could%20be%20strategically%20very%20challenging%20for%20India%20as%20it%20allows%20China%20to%20use%20the%20port%20for%20monitoring%20Indian%20movements%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%20though%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20non-viable%20infrastructure%20constructed%20by%20China%20in%20South%20Asia%20is%20Pakistan's%20Gwadar%20Airport.%20Opened%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20Beijing%20has%20invested%20around%20%24240%20million%20in%20the%20project.%20The%20airport%20can%20handle%20about%204%20lakh%20passengers%20and%20was%20inaugurated%20virtually%20given%20the%20security%20concerns.%20What%20complicates%20the%20matter%20here%20is%20that%20Balochistan%20has%20been%20increasingly%20facing%20rising%20violent%20attacks%2C%20most%20of%20them%20targeted%20towards%20Chinese%20investments%20and%20nationals.%20Due%20to%20these%20security%20challenges%2C%20the%20airport%20has%20witnessed%20no%20flights%20and%20has%20catered%20to%20no%20passengers%20even%20after%20months%20of%20being%20operational.%20Only%2C%20it%20adds%20to%20the%20debt%20woes%20of%20Islamabad%20while%20providing%20Beijing%20with%20another%20crucial%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaldives'%20Chinese%20Tilt%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20investments%20in%20Maldives%20have%20been%20gaining%20momentum%20since%20the%20Muizzu%20government%20has%20taken%20office.%20Since%20Mohammed%20Muizzu's%20explosive%20%E2%80%98India%20Out'%20campaign%2C%20the%20Maldives%20has%20seen%20a%20clear%20tilt%20towards%20Beijing.%20However%2C%20one%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20fact%20that%20in%202016%2C%20the%20island%20nation%20had%20leased%20out%20Feydhoo%20Finolhu%20to%20China%20for%20a%20period%20of%2050%20years%20for%20%244%20million.%20China%20is%20Maldives'%20single%20largest%20lender%2C%20and%20it%20owes%20Beijing%20around%20%241.3%20billion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20undertaken%20a%20number%20of%20infrastructure%20investments%20in%20the%20Maldives%20and%20both%20countries%20have%20even%20adopted%20a%20defence%20cooperation%20deal%2C%20the%20latest%20flagship%20project%20being%20the%20China-Maldives%20friendship%20bridge%2C%20towards%20which%20Beijing%20has%20invested%20around%20%24200%20million.%20No%20surprises%20that%20Xiang%20Yang%20Hong%203%2C%20the%20Chinese%20spy%20vessel%2C%20docked%20for%20%E2%80%98refuelling'%20in%20Male%20in%20February%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EElsewhere%20In%20Bangladesh%20And%20Myanmar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20invested%20heavily%20in%20port%20projects%20in%20Bangladesh%20too%E2%80%94according%20to%20reports%2C%20a%20whopping%20%247%20billion.%20But%20notably%20here%2C%20though%20Beijing%20did%20invest%20in%20the%20development%20of%20Chittagong%20and%20Payra%20ports%2C%20India%20enjoys%20access%20to%20them.%20In%202016%2C%20Chinese%20companies%20had%20even%20agreed%20to%20extend%20around%20%24600%20million%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20main%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20Pyara%20port.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20recent%20political%20changes%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20the%20ouster%20of%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20government%20have%20put%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20India-Bangladesh%20relations.%20The%20existing%20interim%20government%20has%20shown%20its%20keenness%20to%20be%20closer%20to%20Beijing.%20It%20wasn't%20too%20shocking%20when%20after%20years%2C%20a%20Chinese%20naval%20ship%20docked%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Chittagong%20port%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20In%20addition%2C%20Beijing%20has%20also%20announced%20that%20it%20is%20keen%20to%20extend%20a%20loan%20of%20%24335%20million%20for%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20Mongla%20Port%2C%20a%20project%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20undertaken%20by%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20Chinese%20access%20to%20these%20ports%20will%20create%20a%20challenge%20for%20India's%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20China%20was%20also%20looking%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20development%20of%20Myanmar's%20Kyaukphyu%20Deep-Sea%20Port%20and%20the%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20under%20the%20BRI.%20However%2C%20the%20ongoing%20turmoil%20in%20Myanmar%20has%20derailed%20this%20project.%20But%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20restart%20the%20project%2C%20executives%20from%20Chinese%20state-owned%20firm%20CITIC%20Ltd%20recently%20met%20with%20junta%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENepal%20Is%20In%20A%20Pickle%2C%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pokhara%20airport%20in%20Nepal%20was%20built%20with%20Chinese%20loans%20amounting%20to%20%24215%20million.%20The%20airport%20is%20closely%20linked%20to%20Nepalese%20aspirations%20to%20develop%20tourism%20around%20Pokhara.%20There%20have%20been%20reports%20about%20its%20allegedly%20substandard%20construction%20which%20have%20also%20led%20to%20challenges%20with%20functioning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENepal%20has%20been%20hoping%20to%20convert%20these%20loans%20to%20aid%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%20In%20addition%2C%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20loan%20is%20being%20serviced%20at%20a%20rate%20of%205%25%20and%20not%202%25%2C%20as%20was%20publicly%20claimed%20by%20China.%20Also%2C%20given%20that%20the%20airport%20is%20close%20to%20the%20Indian%20border%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20been%20reluctant%20to%20grant%20rights%20to%20use%20its%20airspace%2C%20adding%20to%20Nepal's%20operational%20difficulties.%20The%20airport%20was%20started%20on%20January%201%20in%202023%2C%20and%20has%20not%20witnessed%20more%20than%20a%20few%20flights%2C%20making%20it%20financially%20unviable.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20only%20increased%20Nepal's%20dependence%20on%20China%3A%20tourism%20entrepreneurs%20of%20Pokhara%20and%20Chengdu%20city%20of%20Sichuan%20Province%20met%20recently%20on%20March%2020%20to%20conclude%20an%20agreement%20for%20more%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EExploiting%20Aspirations%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerges%20is%20a%20clear%20pattern%E2%80%94of%20how%20these%20smaller%20nations%20have%20had%20to%20rely%20on%20China%20to%20fulfil%20their%20aspirations%20for%20economic%20and%20infrastructural%20growth%20and%20prosperity%2C%20only%20to%20end%20up%20in%20a%20strategically%20vulnerable%20position.%20Most%20of%20the%20airports%20mentioned%20above%20were%20built%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20enhance%20tourism%20in%20their%20respective%20countries%2C%20and%2C%20thus%2C%20boost%20the%20domestic%20economies.%20But%20given%20their%20current%20state%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20wrong%20to%20argue%20that%20China%20might%20have%20exploited%20these%20nations%20with%20the%20help%20of%20its%20own%20deep%20pockets%2C%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwin-win%E2%80%9D%20BRI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20rate%20of%20interest%20that%20China%20charges%20makes%20it%20impossible%20for%20many%20of%20these%20countries%20to%20repay%20their%20debts%20in%20time%2C%20thus%20getting%20trapped%20in%20a%20debt%20cycle%2C%20which%20ultimately%20endangers%20their%20sovereignty.%20China%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20only%20benefited%20from%20this%20strategically%3A%20most%20of%20these%20projects%20were%20destined%20for%20doom%2C%20and%20thus%20provided%20China%20with%20an%20opportunity%20to%20gain%20an%20edge%20in%20the%20region.%20True%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20Beijing%20doesn't%20have%20any%20direct%20military%20or%20strategic%20presence%20at%20most%20of%20these%20sites.%20But%20its%20naval%20ships%20have%20made%20regular%20forays%20into%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20region%2C%20with%20these%20visits%20having%20only%20grown%20in%20number%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20India%20will%20have%20to%20be%20careful%2C%20and%20on%20alert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20Professor%20at%20OP%20Jindal%20Global%20University)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743148500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Fgwadar-port_650x400_61513519476.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-china-is-exploiting-failed-projects-in-indias-neighbourhood-8030686%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Pakistan%20to%20Nepal%20to%20Myanmar%2C%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20Chinese-financed%20projects%20in%20India's%20neighbourhood%20are%20giving